  "text": "Normalizes meetings, transcripts, attendees, and action items from Gong, Zoom, Teams, Otter, Fireflies, Fathom, and other note-taker systems into one reusable meeting-intelligence payload for prep, coaching, and QBR workflows. Trigger: Schedule / Webhook | Output: Canonical meeting intelligence event + QA alert How it works: [{\"step\":1,\"name\":\"Receive Meeting Artifacts\",\"description\":\"Collects completed meeting events, transcripts, summaries, and action items through polling or webhooks.\",\"type\":\"trigger\",\"color\":\"green\"},{\"step\":2,\"name\":\"Fetch Source Payloads\",\"description\":\"Pulls calendar metadata, attendee lists, transcript snippets, summaries, and action items from the chosen source family.\",\"type\":\"data\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"step\":3,\"name\":\"Normalize Meeting Schema\",\"description\":\"Maps source-specific payloads into canonical meeting fields used by prep, coaching, and follow-up workflows.\",\"type\":\"data\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"step\":4,\"name\":\"Resolve Account Association\",\"description\":\"Matches the meeting to accounts, opportunities, owners, and contacts using attendee, domain, or CRM context.\",\"type\":\"data\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"step\":5,\"name\":\"AI Transcript QA\",\"description\":\"AI Agent flags weak transcripts, missing attendees, ambiguous action items, or poor account mapping before the event is reused downstream.\",\"type\":\"ai\",\"color\":\"purple\"},{\"step\":6,\"name\":\"Publish Canonical Meeting Event\",\"description\":\"Routes the normalized meeting object to meeting-prep, QBR, coaching, or handoff workflows.\",\"type\":\"output\",\"color\":\"orange\"}] Platforms: n8n, recipe-card, n8n-starter, workato, zapier, claude-workflow, openai-workflow",
