  "title": "Multi-Channel Delivery Router (Auto flow)",
  "text": "Receives a ready-to-send insight payload, resolves whether it should land in Slack, Teams, email, or a webhook, adapts the format for that surface, and applies fallback routing without cloning the business logic for each tool. Trigger: Webhook / Sub-workflow | Output: Delivered insight payload across Slack, Teams, Email, or webhook How it works: [{\"step\":1,\"name\":\"Receive Insight Payload\",\"description\":\"Accepts a formatted message plus routing metadata from another workflow, application, or queue.\",\"type\":\"trigger\",\"color\":\"green\"},{\"step\":2,\"name\":\"Resolve Destination\",\"description\":\"Looks up the correct target surface based on account, owner, role, region, or customer segment.\",\"type\":\"data\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"step\":3,\"name\":\"Adapt Message Format\",\"description\":\"Transforms the same insight into Slack-safe markdown, Teams-safe copy/cards, email HTML/plain text, or webhook-safe JSON envelopes.\",\"type\":\"ai\",\"color\":\"purple\"},{\"step\":4,\"name\":\"Deliver to Preferred Channel\",\"description\":\"Sends the adapted payload to the chosen channel using the first-party connector or generic webhook/SMTP action.\",\"type\":\"output\",\"color\":\"orange\"},{\"step\":5,\"name\":\"Apply Fallback Route\",\"description\":\"If delivery fails, routes the message to a backup surface and logs the original failure reason.\",\"type\":\"output\",\"color\":\"orange\"}] Platforms: n8n, recipe-card, n8n-starter, workato, zapier, claude-workflow, openai-workflow",
